Hello all

There is nothing worse than seeing someone we care about going through
something difficult and wanting to help but not knowing how to! Recognizing
the fact that many people out there want to help and there are many others
who want our help, Saathi and Medall Behavioral Health Services are
organizing an E2On Being a HelperE2 workshop to help you reco
gnize signs of
people with suicidal intentions and equipping you with techniques for
intervention.

We rise by lifting up others, so sign up and, show you care!

